  "StockRole": "Skirmisher",
  "YangsThoughts": "Defiance built this in 3151 to mark 500 years of the original Sentinel and it is a serious upgrade in every respect. Rotary AC/5, Streak SRM 6, MASC, Ballistic-Reinforced armor. The Maskirovka apparently agreed it was worth having because their agents stole the blueprints within a few years and the Capellans were building their own by 3157. That is probably the most honest endorsement a mech design can get.",
